Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • bacnet.Database
  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    A ModelProvider specifically design for the Website Database
    Contains persistent variable, used through all the website. It is loaded for each User, it is not shared by users
    Author:
    UIBC
